text: Nabiyow ama korosuk ixxic: Cagalah anu sin innah yan seehadaytuy Yallak wacyi elle obsima kinniyo, Cagalah sin Yallay fan sin kak seeca inki Yallaay agleyta mali, isi Rabbih angaaraw qaagitaah kay digaalak meesita num, toysa meqe taamay yoobula sinniy Yallah caglisa abay, Kaadu isi Rabbih aba qibaadat num asgalle waay
